title: Pitt kickoff
text:
Georgia Tech's annual Hall of Fame weekend will have an early start with the Pitt kickoff set for 12:30 p.m. Oct. 17 at Bobby Dodd Stadium.
The ACC matchup will be televised on the ACC Network.
Georgia Tech is 4-5 against the Panthers. The Yellow Jackets have won their last two meetings. Their Sugar Bowl meeting in 1955 made history .
The Yellow Jackets will face the Clemson Tigers on the road Saturday at 3:30 p.m. The game will air on ABC or ESPN2, depending on location.
